.TH Command : NEWS
The news command is the local newspaper run by The Deity.
This "morning after" daily recounts
financial exploits,
the telegram traffic between countries,
and political maneuvering
in addition to the chronicling of such mundanities as shelling and attacking.
It's great breakfast reading!
.s1
Type:
.EX news
.s3
or:
.EX news 2
if you only wish to see the news for the last two days.
See also : headlines
